---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Us - OpportunityCenter"
  description="Learn about OpportunityCenter, your gateway to scholarships, jobs, internships, loan schemes, and earning methods in the USA and Europe."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">About OpportunityCenter</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          Your trusted resource for global opportunities
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          
          <p>
            At OpportunityCenter, our mission is to bridge the gap between talented individuals and life-changing opportunities. We believe that access to quality information about scholarships, jobs, internships, loan schemes, and earning methods should be available to everyone, regardless of their background or location.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            We are dedicated to providing comprehensive, accurate, and up-to-date information about opportunities in the USA and Europe, helping our readers advance their education, careers, and financial well-being.
          </p>
          
          <h2>What We Offer</h2>
          
          <p>
            OpportunityCenter is a comprehensive platform that offers detailed information on:
          </p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Full and partial scholarships for undergraduate, graduate, and doctoral studies in prestigious institutions across the USA and Europe.</li>
            <li><strong>Jobs:</strong> Career opportunities for professionals of all levels, from entry-level positions to executive roles.</li>
            <li><strong>Internships:</strong> Paid and unpaid internship programs that provide valuable work experience and professional development.</li>
            <li><strong>Loan Schemes:</strong> Educational and business loan opportunities with favorable terms and conditions.</li>
            <li><strong>Earning Methods:</strong> Alternative ways to earn income, including remote work, freelancing, entrepreneurship, and more.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Our Values</h2>
          
          <p>
            At the core of everything we do are our fundamental values:
          </p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We are committed to providing verified and accurate information that our readers can trust.</li>
            <li><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> We believe that opportunities should be accessible to everyone, regardless of their background, gender, race, or nationality.</li>
            <li><strong>Empowerment:</strong> We aim to empower individuals to take control of their education, career, and financial future.</li>
            <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We continuously seek new ways to improve our platform and provide valuable resources to our readers.</li>
            <li><strong>Community:</strong> We foster a community of like-minded individuals who support and inspire each other.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Our Team</h2>
          
          <p>
            OpportunityCenter is powered by a dedicated team of researchers, writers, and industry experts who are passionate about helping others succeed. Our team members have diverse backgrounds in education, career counseling, finance, and international relations, allowing us to provide comprehensive and insightful content.
          </p>
          
          <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
          
          <p>
            We invite you to join our growing community of opportunity seekers. Subscribe to our newsletter to receive regular updates on the latest opportunities, follow us on social media for daily inspiration, and engage with our content to share your experiences and insights.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Thank you for choosing OpportunityCenter as your trusted resource for global opportunities. We are committed to helping you achieve your goals and realize your full potential.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Team Section (Placeholder) -->
        <div class="mt-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center font-heading text-gray-900 mb-12">Meet Our Team</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Team Member 1 -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-primary-100 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 font-heading">Sarah Johnson</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Founder & CEO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Education specialist with 15+ years of experience in international education.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Team Member 2 -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-primary-100 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 font-heading">Michael Chen</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Head of Research</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Career counselor specialized in international job markets and opportunities.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Team Member 3 -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-primary-100 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 font-heading">Elena Rodriguez</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Content Director</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Writer and editor with expertise in educational content and scholarship programs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Contact CTA -->
        <div class="mt-16 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-heading mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Have questions or want to collaborate with us? We'd love to hear from you!
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-base font-medium text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary-500 transition-colors duration-200">
            Contact Us
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>